<h1>话</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#000099;">huà</span><span class=alesi>(hua4)</span> , hua <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 话 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 话</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/speech" style="color:black;">speech</a>, <a href="/dictionary/talk" style="color:black;">talk</a>, <a href="/dictionary/language" style="color:black;">language</a>; dialect</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 8<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 8 strokes: <a href="/character/的" title="de: possessive, adjectival suffix">的</a>, <a href="/character/和" title="he2: harmony, peace; peaceful, calm">和</a>, <a href="/character/国" title="guo2: nation, country, nation-state">国</a>, <a href="/character/到" title="dao4: go to, arrive, been to">到</a>, <a href="/character/所" title="suo3: place, location; numerary adjunct">所</a>, <a href="/character/事" title="shi4: affair, matter, business; to serve; accident, incident">事</a>, <a href="/character/经" title="jing1: classic works; pass through">经</a>, <a href="/character/法" title="fa3: law, rule, regulation, statute; France, French">法</a>, <a href="/character/学" title="xue2: learning, knowledge; school">学</a>, <a href="/character/现" title="xian4: appear, manifest, become visible">现</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/言" title="Kangxi radical 149">言</a>&nbsp;149.6</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 1 <br><small>Other HSK 1 characters: <a href="/character/月" title="yue4: moon; month; KangXi radical 74">月</a>, <a href="/character/回" title="hui2: return, turn around; a time">回</a>, <a href="/character/西" title="xi1: west(ern); westward, occident">西</a>, <a href="/character/果" title="guo3: fruit; result">果</a>, <a href="/character/老" title="lao3: old, aged; experienced">老</a>, <a href="/character/二" title="er4: two; twice">二</a>, <a href="/character/什" title="shen2: file of ten soldiers; mixed, miscellaneous">什</a>, <a href="/character/见" title="jian4: see, observe, behold; perceive">见</a>, <a href="/character/先" title="xian1: first, former, previous">先</a>, <a href="/character/儿" title="er2: son, child; KangXi radical 10">儿</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-1" tit